  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to asses the efficacy and safety of Telmisartan depending on the
      use of an electronic therapy monitoring device (HelpingHand) in a real life setting and to
      asses patients compliance to the therapy with Telmisartan in relation to use of electronic
      therapy monitoring device.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
